        ### Installation
        ```bash
        $ [sudo] pip install django-env-context-processor
        ```
        
        ##### `settings.py`
        ```python
        TEMPLATES = [
            {
                # â€¦
                'OPTIONS': {
                    'context_processors': [
                        'django_env_context_processor.context_processors.env',
                    ],
                },
            },
        ]
        ```
        
        ##### `.env`
        ```bash
        export ENV_VARIABLE=42
        ```
        
        ##### Templates
        ```html
        {{ ENV_VARIABLE }}
        ```
        
